      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "While we’re not too surprised by the Mustang’s global success, it was interesting to learn EcoBoost and GT models weren’t driving the sales surge last year. According to Ford, it was the Bullitt, ",
