            "text": "Undoubtedly, excitement over the new and quite fantastic Shelby GT500 drove a fair amount of that sales growth last year. Both the Shelby and Bullitt models saw a sales increase of 52.7 percent versus 2019. Ford’s hopeful the launch of the Mustang Mach 1 will keep driving that kind of success.",
